3)write the program for arithmetic series 1 4 7 10.....
series = [1, 4, 7]
for i in range(3,30):
series.append(series[i-1] + 3)
print(series)
4)write a program to a sum of the series 1**3+2**3+3**3+4**3+.....n
n = int(input(&quot;Enter the value of n: &quot;))
sum = 0
for i in range(1, n+1):

sum = sum + i**3
print(&quot;Sum of the series is:&quot;, sum)
