11)write a program to find the sum of the series 1!+2!+3!+..+n!
n = int(input(&#39;Enter the value of n: &#39;))
sum = 0
for i in range(1, n+1):
fact = 1
for j in range(1, i+1):
fact = fact * j
sum += fact
print(&#39;The sum of the series is&#39;,sum)
12)write a program for to find the sum of the series 9+99+999+9999+...+n
n = int(input(&quot;Enter the no of terms: &quot;))
sum = 0
for i in range(1, n+1):
sum = sum + ((10**i)-1)

print(&quot;Sum of series is: &quot;,sum)
